snippet.title: Battalion 1944 -  Early Access Trailer 2018
snippet.description:
World War 2 multiplayer FPS Battalion 1944 will be coming to Early Access on February 1st! 
Add to your Steam wishlist here: http://steamcommunity.com/games/489940
Sign-up to the closed beta here: http://beta.battaliongame.com
